(189, 3, '2013-11-27 07:33:54', '2013-11-27 07:33:54', 'Synchronicity and moonlight will transform the much loved Melbourne City Baths into a special performance space. Teams of synchronised swimmers from Victorian Synchronised Swimming Incorporated (VSSI) will perform throughout the night showcasing this exquisite sport. As part of the new Northern Lights precinct, <i>Moonlight Synchro</i> brings together elegant formations of swimmers in a dramatic, atmospheric setting inside Melbourne’s stunning heritage icon.', 'Moonlight Synchro ', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '163-revision-v1', '', '', '2013-11-27 07:33:54', '2013-11-27 07:33:54', '', 163, 'http://whitenight.dev/163-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(190, 3, '2013-11-27 07:38:00', '2013-11-27 07:38:00', 'Bourke Street Mall, Melbourne’s central shopping strip, will feature a large outdoor stage and be abuzz with music fans. Featuring bands playing tunes from jazz to rhythm and blues, crowds of all ages can delight in the dulcet tones all night. Programmer Julie O’Hara has performed and liaised with big bands, gypsy swing, traditional jazz, R &amp; B, swing bebop and vocalese for almost twenty years.', 'J + R & B', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '165-revision-v1', '', '', '2013-11-27 07:38:00', '2013-11-27 07:38:00', '', 165, 'http://whitenight.dev/165-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
