(202, 3, '2013-11-27 08:00:13', '2013-11-27 08:00:13', 'Using future technology and che-botics, the <em>Print-Bot (Series I)</em> is the newest printing technology brought through the vortex to Earth from planet Chehehe. The user places an object onto the input-tray, it then travels through the Print-Bot and is printed on using Intergalactic Printing Systems (IPS). When the print is complete, the user can retrieve their now transformed object from the output-tray.', 'Print-Bot (Series I)', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'print-bot-series-i', '', '', '2013-11-27 12:19:35', '2013-11-27 12:19:35', '', 0, 'http://whitenight.dev/?post_type=event&#038;p=202', 0, 'event', '', 0),
