(215, 3, '2013-11-27 08:14:52', '2013-11-27 08:14:52', 'Using future technology and che-botics, the <em>Print-Bot (Series I)</em> is the newest printing technology brought through the vortex to Earth from planet Chehehe. The user places an object onto the input-tray, it then travels through the Print-Bot and is printed on using Intergalactic Printing Systems (IPS). When the print is complete, the user can retrieve their now transformed object from the output-tray.', 'Print-Bot (Series I)', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '202-revision-v1', '', '', '2013-11-27 08:14:52', '2013-11-27 08:14:52', '', 202, 'http://whitenight.dev/202-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
